name: Ui-router-lazy-example
tagline: An example showing use of ui-router-extras futureStates with ocLazyLoad to lazy load a requirejs module, which in turn registers an angular module, which in turn loads the new ui-router states.
body: ### Welcome to FutureStates App. A demo of ui-router-extras future states with ozLazyLoad and requirejs.
